<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Your Listening Universe · 2021–2026</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root { --bg:#0a0a0f;--surface:#111118;--surface2:#18181f;--border:#2a2a38;--accent:#c8f55a;--accent2:#7b6cf5;--accent3:#f5c84a;--text:#e8e8f0;--muted:#6b6b80;--serif:'DM Serif Display',serif;--mono:'DM Mono',monospace; }
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
  body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
  body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");pointer-events:none;z-index:100;opacity:0.6}
  header{padding:60px 48px 40px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:24px}
  h1{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem);font-weight:400;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-.02em}
  h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--accent)}
  .header-sub{margin-top:12px;color:var(--muted);font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase}
  .stat-pills{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .pill{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:12px 20px;text-align:center}
  .pill .val{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--accent);line-height:1}
  .pill .lbl{font-size:.65rem;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:4px}
  .tabs{display:flex;padding:0 48px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);overflow-x:auto}
  .tab{padding:18px 24px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;margin-bottom:-1px;white-space:nowrap;transition:all .2s;background:none;border-left:none;border-right:none;border-top:none}
  .tab:hover{color:var(--text)}.tab.active{color:var(--accent);border-bottom-color:var(--accent)}
  .panel{display:none;padding:48px;animation:fadeIn .3s ease}.panel.active{display:block}
  @keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
  .section-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:32px;color:var(--text)}
  .year-tabs{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:32px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .year-tab{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:8px 18px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.75rem;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em}
  .year-tab:hover{color:var(--text)}.year-tab.active{color:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent);background:rgba(200,245,90,.05)}
  .year-panel{display:none}.year-panel.active{display:block;animation:fadeIn .25s ease}
  .year-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px}
  @media(max-width:900px){.year-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .filter-bar{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}
  .search-box{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:10px 16px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text);width:280px;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s}
  .search-box:focus{border-color:var(--accent2)}.search-box::placeholder{color:var(--muted)}
  .sort-btn{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:10px 16px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.75rem;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;transition:all .2s}
  .sort-btn:hover,.sort-btn.active{color:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent)}
  .track-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}
  .track-table th{text-align:left;font-size:.65rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--muted);padding:12px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);cursor:pointer;user-select:none}
  .track-table th:hover{color:var(--accent)}
  .track-table td{padding:14px 16px;font-size:.8rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(42,42,56,.5);vertical-align:middle}
  .track-table tr:hover td{background:var(--surface2)}
  .track-name{font-weight:500;color:var(--text)}.track-artist{color:var(--muted);font-size:.75rem}
  .rank-badge{display:inline-block;width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);text-align:center;line-height:28px;font-size:.7rem;color:var(--muted)}
  .rank-badge.gold{background:rgba(245,200,74,.1);border-color:var(--accent3);color:var(--accent3)}
  .rank-badge.silver{background:rgba(200,200,220,.08);border-color:#aaa;color:#ccc}
  .rank-badge.bronze{background:rgba(180,120,60,.1);border-color:#b97b3c;color:#c8924d}
  .bar-cell{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
  .mini-bar{height:4px;border-radius:2px;background:var(--accent2);min-width:2px}
  .new-badge{display:inline-block;padding:2px 7px;background:rgba(200,245,90,.1);border:1px solid rgba(200,245,90,.3);border-radius:3px;font-size:.55rem;color:var(--accent);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-left:6px;vertical-align:middle}
  .pagination{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:24px;align-items:center;font-size:.75rem;color:var(--muted);flex-wrap:wrap}
  .page-btn{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:6px 12px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.75rem;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
  .page-btn:hover,.page-btn.active{color:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent)}
  .insight-box{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--accent);border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:24px;font-size:.8rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--text)}
  .insight-box strong{color:var(--accent)}
  .chart-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px}
  @media(max-width:900px){.chart-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .chart-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:28px}
  .chart-card.wide{grid-column:1/-1}
  .chart-title{font-size:.7rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:24px}
  canvas{width:100%!important}
  .artist-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
  .artist-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(42,42,56,.4)}
  .artist-rank{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--muted);width:20px;text-align:right}
  .artist-name{flex:1;font-size:.85rem}
  .artist-bar-wrap{flex:2}
  .artist-bar{height:6px;border-radius:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent2),var(--accent));margin-bottom:4px}
  .artist-stats{font-size:.65rem;color:var(--muted)}
  .album-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:16px}
  .album-card{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .2s}
  .album-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent2)}
  .album-rank-bg{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:4rem;color:var(--accent2);opacity:.07;position:absolute;bottom:-10px;right:12px;line-height:1;font-style:italic;pointer-events:none}
  .album-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;line-height:1.2}
  .album-artist{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:12px}
  .album-stats{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--muted)}
  .heatmap{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:4px;height:120px}
  .hour-col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px;flex:1}
  .hour-bar-wrap{flex:1;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;width:100%;height:100px}
  .hour-bar{width:100%;border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;min-height:2px}
  .hour-bar:hover{opacity:.7}
  .hour-label{font-size:.55rem;color:var(--muted)}
  .era-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin-bottom:32px}
  @media(max-width:700px){.era-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
  .era-card{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:20px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .era-year-bg{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:3rem;color:var(--accent2);opacity:.12;position:absolute;bottom:-4px;right:10px;line-height:1;pointer-events:none;font-style:italic}
  .era-hrs{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.4rem;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:10px}
  .era-artist-line{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:3px}
  .era-artist-line strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:500}
  .mini-track-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  .mini-track-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(42,42,56,.4)}
  .mini-rank{font-size:.65rem;color:var(--muted);width:16px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0}
  .mini-info{flex:1;min-width:0}
  .mini-name{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text);font-weight:500;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
  .mini-sub{font-size:.65rem;color:var(--muted)}
  .mini-stat{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0;text-align:right}
  .year-stat-row{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:24px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .year-stat{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:10px 16px}
  .year-stat .v{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--accent);line-height:1.1}
  .year-stat .l{font-size:.6rem;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:3px}

  /* ── Genre clusters ── */
  .genre-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px;align-items:start}
  @media(max-width:900px){.genre-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .genre-legend{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
  .genre-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(42,42,56,.4)}
  .genre-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
  .genre-name{flex:1;font-size:.82rem}
  .genre-hrs{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0}
  .genre-artists{font-size:.62rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}

  /* ── Discovery vs Loyalty ── */
  .loyalty-scatter-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;height:360px}
  .loyalty-dot{position:absolute;border-radius:50%;cursor:default;transition:transform .15s}
  .loyalty-dot:hover{transform:scale(1.3);z-index:10}
  .loyalty-axis-x{position:absolute;bottom:28px;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:var(--border)}
  .loyalty-axis-y{position:absolute;left:60px;top:0;bottom:28px;width:1px;background:var(--border)}
  .loyalty-label-x{position:absolute;bottom:8px;font-size:.6rem;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em}
  .loyalty-label-y{position:absolute;font-size:.6rem;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;transform-origin:left center;transform:rotate(-90deg)}
  .loyalty-tooltip{position:absolute;background:#0e0e18;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:8px 12px;font-size:.7rem;pointer-events:none;display:none;z-index:20;white-space:nowrap}
  .loyalty-tooltip strong{color:var(--accent);display:block;margin-bottom:2px}

  /* ── Listener Portrait ── */
  .portrait-wrap{display:flex;justify-content:center;padding:16px 0 40px}
  .portrait-card{width:100%;max-width:540px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0e0e1a 0%,#14122a 60%,#0e1a0e 100%);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:44px 44px 36px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .portrait-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 0%,rgba(123,108,245,.18) 0%,transparent 55%),radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 90%,rgba(200,245,90,.1) 0%,transparent 50%);pointer-events:none}
  .portrait-eyebrow{font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:20px}
  .portrait-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:3rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--text);line-height:1;margin-bottom:6px}
  .portrait-years{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:32px}
  .portrait-quote{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.25rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:32px;position:relative;padding-left:20px}
  .portrait-quote::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:4px;bottom:4px;width:2px;background:var(--accent);border-radius:2px}
  .portrait-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(--border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:28px}
  .portrait-stat{background:#0e0e1a;padding:14px 12px;text-align:center}
  .portrait-stat .pv{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.6rem;color:var(--accent);line-height:1}
  .portrait-stat .pl{font-size:.55rem;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:4px}
  .portrait-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px}
  .portrait-tag{padding:5px 12px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;font-size:.65rem;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase}
  .portrait-tag.lit{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);background:rgba(200,245,90,.06)}
  .portrait-watermark{position:absolute;bottom:20px;right:28px;font-family:var(--serif);font-size:5rem;color:var(--accent2);opacity:.05;font-style:italic;line-height:1;pointer-events:none;user-select:none}

  /* ── Skip psychology ── */
  .skip-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px}
  @media(max-width:900px){.skip-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .skip-grid .chart-card.wide{grid-column:1/-1}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div>
    <h1>Your Listening <em>Universe</em></h1>
    <div class="header-sub">Spotify · Extended History · 2021–2026</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-pills">
    <div class="pill"><div class="val">54,764</div><div class="lbl">Total streams</div></div>
    <div class="pill"><div class="val">1,657h</div><div class="lbl">Total listening</div></div>
    <div class="pill"><div class="val">99h</div><div class="lbl">Top artist (hrs)</div></div>
    <div class="pill"><div class="val">349</div><div class="lbl">Most-played track</div></div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="tabs">
  <button class="tab active" onclick="switchTab('tracks',this)">Songs</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('albums',this)">Albums</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('artists',this)">Artists</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('timeline',this)">Timeline</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('eras',this)">By Year</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('patterns',this)">Patterns</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('genres',this)">Vibes</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('loyalty',this)">Loyalty</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('portrait',this)">Portrait</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab('skips',this)">Skip Psychology</button>
</div>

<div id="tracks" class="panel active">
  <div class="section-title">Your Most-Played Songs</div>
  <div class="insight-box">A new all-time #1 across the full timeline: <strong>Baby Girl by Disco Lines</strong> — 616 minutes, 349 plays, under 5% skip rate. That's a different kind of love than Jai Paul's Genevieve (Unfinished) at #2. One you stay inside completely. The other you return to restlessly. Both are devotion. Different kinds.</div>
  <div class="filter-bar">
    <input class="search-box" id="trackSearch" placeholder="Search track or artist…" oninput="filterTracks()">
    <button class="sort-btn active" id="sortTime" onclick="sortTracks('mins')">Sort: Time</button>
    <button class="sort-btn" id="sortPlays" onclick="sortTracks('plays')">Sort: Plays</button>
    <button class="sort-btn" id="sortSkips" onclick="sortTracks('skips')">Sort: Skips</button>
    <button class="sort-btn" id="sortRate" onclick="sortTracks('rate')">Sort: Skip %</button>
  </div>
  <table class="track-table">
    <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>Track</th><th onclick="sortTracks('mins')">Minutes ↕</th><th onclick="sortTracks('plays')">Plays ↕</th><th onclick="sortTracks('skips')">Skips ↕</th><th>Engagement</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody id="trackBody"></tbody>
  </table>
  <div class="pagination" id="pagination"></div>
</div>

<div id="albums" class="panel">
  <div class="section-title">Your Most-Played Albums</div>
  <div class="insight-box"><strong>Jai Paul's Leak 04-13 (Bait Ones)</strong> is your most-played album at 45 hours — a collection of unfinished, leaked demos you've listened to more than any complete, intentional release. Pink Floyd appears three times in the top 25. Johnny Goth has five albums in the top 30.</div>
  <div class="album-grid" id="albumGrid"></div>
</div>

<div id="artists" class="panel">
  <div class="section-title">Artists Who Defined Your Era</div>
  <div class="insight-box"><strong>Johnny Goth at 99 hours</strong> is a number without comparison — that's not an artist you listen to, that's an atmosphere you live inside. Pink Floyd's rise to #3 is entirely a 2024 story. Artemas at #5 is 2025 breaking through.</div>
  <div class="artist-list" id="artistList"></div>
</div>

<div id="timeline" class="panel">
  <div class="section-title">How Your Listening Changed Over Time</div>
  <div class="insight-box">The silence of mid-2022 followed by the explosion of summer 2023 remains the most dramatic arc. <strong>August 2023: 120 hours.</strong> Then 2024 settled into sustained rhythm. Something stabilized after the intensity broke open.</div>
  <div class="chart-card wide"><div class="chart-title">Monthly listening hours · 2021–2026</div><canvas id="timelineChart" height="70"></canvas></div>
</div>

<div id="eras" class="panel">
  <div class="section-title">Your Listening Eras</div>
  <div class="insight-box">Each year is a different version of you. <strong>2022</strong> was singular — deep Johnny Goth atmosphere. <strong>2023</strong> was the year everything opened (533 hours). <strong>2024</strong> brought patience and Pink Floyd. <strong>2025</strong> arrived with Artemas leading for the first time.</div>
  <div class="year-tabs">
    <button class="year-tab active" onclick="switchYear('overview',this)">Overview</button>
    <button class="year-tab" onclick="switchYear('2021',this)">2021</button>
    <button class="year-tab" onclick="switchYear('2022',this)">2022</button>
    <button class="year-tab" onclick="switchYear('2023',this)">2023</button>
    <button class="year-tab" onclick="switchYear('2024',this)">2024</button>
    <button class="year-tab" onclick="switchYear('2025',this)">2025</button>
    <button class="year-tab" onclick="switchYear('2026',this)">2026</button>
  </div>
  <div id="year-overview" class="year-panel active">
    <div class="era-grid" id="eraGrid"></div>
    <div class="chart-card wide"><div class="chart-title">Total hours per year</div><canvas id="yearChart" height="60"></canvas></div>
  </div>
  <div id="year-2021" class="year-panel"></div>
  <div id="year-2022" class="year-panel"></div>
  <div id="year-2023" class="year-panel"></div>
  <div id="year-2024" class="year-panel"></div>
  <div id="year-2025" class="year-panel"></div>
  <div id="year-2026" class="year-panel"></div>
</div>

<div id="patterns" class="panel">
  <div class="section-title">When You Listen</div>
  <div class="insight-box">Across 4+ years the pattern never wavered: <strong>you are a creature of the night.</strong> Midnight to 5am is your heaviest listening window. The 10am–1pm silence is near-total and consistent.</div>
  <div class="chart-grid">
    <div class="chart-card wide"><div class="chart-title">Listening intensity by hour of day (UTC)</div><div class="heatmap" id="heatmap"></div></div>
    <div class="chart-card"><div class="chart-title">Top 10 tracks — plays vs minutes</div><canvas id="scatterChart" height="200"></canvas></div>
    <div class="chart-card"><div class="chart-title">Most devoted tracks — lowest skip rate (min 50 plays)</div><canvas id="devotionChart" height="200"></canvas></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- VIBES / GENRE CLUSTERS -->
<div id="genres" class="panel">
  <div class="section-title">Vibe Clusters</div>
  <div class="insight-box">Your listening breaks into five distinct emotional territories. <strong>Dark indie / post-punk</strong> dominates at over 200 hours — Johnny Goth, Daughter, Provoker, the gravity at the center of everything. Psychedelic rock arrived quietly in 2024 and never left. Electronic and hypnagogic pop thread through every era.</div>
  <div class="genre-layout">
    <div class="chart-card"><div class="chart-title">Hours by vibe</div><canvas id="genreDonut" height="280"></canvas></div>
    <div class="chart-card"><div class="chart-title">Vibe breakdown</div><div class="genre-legend" id="genreLegend"></div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- DISCOVERY VS LOYALTY -->
<div id="loyalty" class="panel">
  <div class="section-title">Discovery vs. Loyalty</div>
  <div class="insight-box">Tracks that appear across <strong>multiple years</strong> are your anchors — songs you keep returning to long after discovery. Tracks that blaze in one year and vanish are moments. The most loyal tracks in your data span 3–4 years of continuous return. Hover any dot for details.</div>
  <div class="chart-card wide">
    <div class="chart-title">Track lifespan · x = total plays · y = years active · size = total minutes</div>
